{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Playstyle.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Grocery Store Tycoon allows the user to play as the owner in first person view while also being able to manage the store from above with free camera movement.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Zoom_Gif.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Checkout.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Operate the Cash Register yourself if you would like to challenge the speed of your best cashier, or simply do not want to pay the wage. Swipe as fast as you can to avoid long queue times and unhappy customers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Checkout_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Stocking.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Stock Shelves by carrying a case at a time from the warehouse or use a cart to transport larger quantities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Stocking_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Customize.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Purchase Placeables such as Cash Registers, Shelving, Coolers, Freezers, Produce Shelves, Shopping Cart Corrals, Shopping Basket Stands, Material Handling Equipment, and Decorations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Cusomization_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/UI.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Interactive UI to manage your store through customer statistics, supply and demand of goods, pricing adjustments, placeable condition viewing, and employee management.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/UI_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Progress.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Unlock Item Types, Placeables, Management Tools, Employee Hiring Capacity, Store Expansions, and the opportunity to purchase other stores by gaining experience passively, by working, or by completing bonus objectives.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Progress_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Maintanence.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Maintain placeables, return carts and baskets, and keep the store clean to keep your store operating at its full potential.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Maintanence_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Employee.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Manage Employees to keep them happy or they may quit! Assigning an employee to the job they would like, the wage they want, and not overworking them all contribute to the employee's happiness. Unreliable employees may call in and affect your happiness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Employee_GIF_2.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Customer.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Customers must be satisfied to get good reviews and keep your store in good standing. Having the goods they seek, keeping them in the store for as little time as possible, and  having a charismatic employee behind the cash register all contribute to the satisfaction of customers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Customer_GIF.gif?t=1738924176\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738924176","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738924176","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/f2eb4bfb96566d8927153f56f404e3cdec02af1a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738924176","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/f2eb4bfb96566d8927153f56f404e3cdec02af1a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738924176","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3222090,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Playstyle.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Grocery Store Tycoon allows the user to play as the owner in first person view while also being able to manage the store from above with free camera movement.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Zoom_Gif.gif?t=1738924176\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870330/extras/Checkout.png?t=1738924176\" /><br>Operate the Cash Register yourself if you would like to challenge the speed of your best cashier, or simply do not want to pay the wage. Swipe as fast as you